title: 820-02016 5v  PPBUS_AON 1v
message:
Remove F5200 and check C5254 voltage.
If still missing, post U5200 voltages: pins P_IN, AUX_DET, SMC_RST_IN, VDDA/P, EN_MVR, AUX_OK, A/BMON.

message:

title: 820-02016 5v  PPBUS_AON 1v
message: sorry diode mode on PPVBAT is 500 and on PPBUS is 110

title: 820-02016 5v  PPBUS_AON 1v
message:
Check diode mode to ground on all coils.
Pay atention to 3V8_AON and 3V3_S2.
Also check at PMUs LDOs.

BTW, check resistance between PPBUS_AON and all coils too.

title: 820-02016 5v  PPBUS_AON 1v
